long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Webbie shows your time spent on your current website and also lists your top five most used webistes.

No ads, no in-app purchases, just simple web tracking. Webbie is an open source project: https://github.com/ColtonQ/webbie
